{"tid":1509190,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"救下我唔該⋯","createTime":"2019-08-26T18:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T18:08:51.000Z","uid":308774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dec4b61fdd6eec7e4e282473c9f7841c852ecbc9","tid":1509190,"uid":308774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:01:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱先見到個中學生po話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢想去救人但係俾其他手足叫佢自己去...</span>結果條友真係自己去咗<br />\n我先唔評論佢落單衝動差啲俾人捉嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我想講佢呢啲先係真正<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線應有心態</span><br />\n當然我唔鼓吹盲目衝出去送頭叫救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係都好希望大家有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">齊上齊落</span></span>心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線少一個冇一個<br />\n唔希望大家一出畜龍防暴就想返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係望一望後面睇下其他手足安唔安全<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救得一個得一個<br />\n我哋齊上齊落好冇？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應承我唔好拋低仼何一個手足好冇？</span>"},{"pid":"0b1fe49df8c5849eabb7b6ca39f51047b2a54dc4","tid":1509190,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=c35fd63a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=aa5f8396\" data-auto-link 